720374f-b.text:
Henry Street, west from Gouverneur Street. At the right is the four story building housing Engine Co. 15. This adjoins the playground on Gouverneur Street which extends northward to East Broadway. These two features are detailed in View No. 2.
June 24, 1939
No's. 1-2
P. L. Sperr
